Oh yea i forgot how Tchalla is a pussy as bitch who'd let some...
body:
“Steve rogers willing to sacrifice wakanda for 1 dumb robot”

Oh yea i forgot how Tchalla is a pussy as bitch who’d let some white bitch from brooklyn put his ppl in danger. Your flippant attempt to shit on the writers makes Tchalla look like a bitch and not the noble king he is. The entire UNIVERSE was in danger and Earth was the battleground. And wakanda was Earths greatest hope and they almost won anyways. You think the black panther is going to do nothing when Wakanda has the best tech best scientists and best fighters in the solar system?

And whats with this bullshit about vision. They arent sacrificing lives for 1 robot. They are trying to save the universe without some dark sacrifice like The One Who Walks Away From Omelas or The Lottery. Do you not undestand the difference between sacrifice and self sacrifice. The good guys dont strsight up stand in a room and agree to execute someone to save the universe at least not as a plan A

And you know Vision is a Person right? Even if he was Just a robit this shitty site is full of ppl wanting to fuck robots or fight for their rights or both.

Yall just petty bitches
